{"tid":1692660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"表楊黨鐵黃衫同黑衫力架","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T07:48:31.000Z","uid":30412,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ec5424ca6edc01aed08553c14540593cdbac33","tid":1692660,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"細佬琴晚去左太古朋友到打機 離開需要經黨鐵站上返康山 <br />\n點知臨走成班著綠色衫既煙剷對住地鐵站入口噴煙 我同啲朋友走都走唔切 衝晒入黨鐵站避難<br />\n之後一入到去黨鐵大堂 成班黃衫 同黑衫力架 <br />\n又衝埋黎睇吓我地有咩要幫手 又派水又教我地要噴口水可以去埋邊<br />\n只係想講 其實爆黨鐵啲野 佢地冇所謂 不過唔好當前線職員係敵人 佢地好多好好人 我都估唔到黑衫都會幫我地"},{"pid":"938970069fb71c88cce51964dc1739e8f94afe46","tid":1692660,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:45:42.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"339f8bea9316e05034342c21108b6540208607b6","tid":1692660,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"嫌國際戰線唔夠難打？<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"270e5a9161138a996cd8e45d70be30e24a4b65dc","tid":1692660,"uid":30412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339f8bea9316e05034342c21108b6540208607b6","tid":1692660,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"嫌國際戰線唔夠難打？<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe737241bebd4981cc752a06f7f85f72cec7182","tid":1692660,"uid":234232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:48:31.000Z","msg":"咁不如唔好再咁稱呼人地？"}]}